{
  "texts": [
    "Here, more than 40 works have employed CNN and remaining have employed other DL techniques such as RNN, generative models etc.",
    "Figure 8 shows the distribution of the different DL models in detail.",
    "It is evident from them that CNN models are more popular than others.",
    "The CNNs are today used unanimously for image classification task, they extract features from a highdimensional image data without losing much of the information.",
    "However, the focus has to now shift on contriving of other DL models that addresses the challenges of longitudinal data presented by the multimodal diagnostic data of the AD."
  ]
}